Here you will find instructions to manage the translation of "Open Education
Handbook".

Requirements
------------

- [Translate
  Toolkit](http://docs.translatehouse.org/projects/translate-toolkit/en/latest/installation.html)
- [Transifex
  Client](http://support.transifex.com/customer/portal/articles/995605-installation)

Fetch the translation
---------------------

~~~
$ ./fetch.sh https://www.transifex.com username password
~~~

You should find a directory named `open-education-handbook` with all the data
from Transifex.

Initial Setup
-------------

This should be only use in the first setup of the translation.

~~~
$ ./setup.sh https://www.transifex.com username password
~~~

The script should download the "Open Education Handbook" from BookType, create
POT files and upload it to Transifex.
